rComments: He's a really nice guy and explains things pretty well. Small class so you get to discuss things with everyone. Tests and problem sets are very fair. Take his tip and really study those EA exams for finals!!

Amazing prof. Very knowledgeable, he's been in the pension industry for several years and is probably the best to teach this course. Super nice, he's within reach if you need help. He also teaches the 2nd part of ACT473, awesome lectures as well. I would definitely recommend to take those courses with Prof Lyons.
